  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "キティとのコミュニケーションを中心にしたゲームで、会話を楽しむことができます。アクションパートではミニゲームをプレイしたり、アイテムを集めて部屋を再装飾することができます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "A Hello Kitty puzzle and mini game collection.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "In this game the player is able to manage and overlook a house owned by Hello Kitty known as Happy House. The player can decorate the Happy House with furniture and this can influence the way Hello Kitty behaves. Furthermore, as the game progresses the player is able to teach Hello Kitty new words.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
